As the sentencing of convicted paedophile Collan Rex‚ a former assistant water polo coach at Parktown Boys’ High‚ was postponed on Wednesday‚ it emerged that 98 teachers were fired in the last financial year for a host of serious offences‚ including having sexual relationships with pupils. A further 483 teachers from six provinces were slapped with final written warnings and 308 with fines‚ while 119 were suspended without pay. 